cz.cuni.mff.kocur.console

Class ConsoleManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • cz.cuni.mff.kocur.console.ConsoleManager

  • public class ConsoleManager
extends Object
    Class that manages the Controllables and the ConsolePanel and the CommandHistory. Controllables should be objects, that allow the console to control them. ConsolePanel displays the console. CommandHistory stores history of commands, so ConsolePanel can use them for better usability.
    Author:
    kocur
